{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/BeginOrnament.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a journey to Mars, where you are the pioneer of a new era. Struggle against the ruthless Martian terrain to establish a self-sustaining colony. Balance resource management and societal advancement to ensure the survival and prosperity of your settlers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Martian_colony_simulation_Header.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/First.gif?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Envision the future and sculpt a resilient colony. Strategically utilize its resources to cultivate a scalable, self-sustaining society. Your management will dictate the growth and prosperity of a new civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Icons.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Intricate_Electrical_System_Header.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Electricity.gif?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harness the solar and wind power, integrate nuclear power, and construct a dependable electricity grid. Utilize battery storage to maintain base operations during the dark hours, ensuring a seamless power transition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Off-Earth_Farming_Header.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Greenhouse.gif?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the Meals Ready to Eat reserves will quickly run out, create efficient greenhouses to ensure your colonist\u2019s survival. Improve off-Earth technologies using hydroponics and aquaponics to enhance crop growth and a sustainable use of resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Complex_gas_simulation_Header.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Overlays.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Actively monitor and manage real-time Oxygen and CO2 levels to keep your colonists alive. Regulate temperature for a comfortable and cozy habitat, ensuring your settlers' well-being and happiness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Day_and_night_cycle_Header.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Day_and_night_cropped.gif?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plan your colony's activities in sync with the Martian day, leveraging light and darkness to your advantage. Create schedules that align with natural light cycles, optimizing energy usage and enhancing the productivity of your colonists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Research_and_Developement_Header.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Research.gif?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you establish your colony, research becomes a cornerstone of progress. From developing efficient energy solutions to pioneering new construction methods, your ability to innovate will define the future of your colony.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Crew_Management_Header.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Socialisation_cropped.gif?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the unforgiving Martian landscape, your colonists are your greatest resource. Manage a complex system of skills, traits, and relationships as you guide your crew through the challenges of off-world living. Monitor their physical health and mental states, ensuring they remain resilient in the face of adversity. Create a thriving community where each colonist's unique abilities contribute to the greater good of the colony.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And more...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/EndOrnament.png?t=1730066206\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730066206","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/page.bg.jpg?t=1730066206","capsule_image":"https://shared