s/Day_and_night_cycle_Header.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Day_and_night_cropped.gif?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plan your colony's activities in sync with the Martian day, leveraging light and darkness to your advantage. Create schedules that align with natural light cycles, optimizing energy usage and enhancing the productivity of your colonists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Research_and_Developement_Header.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Research.gif?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you establish your colony, research becomes a cornerstone of progress. From developing efficient energy solutions to pioneering new construction methods, your ability to innovate will define the future of your colony.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Crew_Management_Header.png?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536140/extras/Socialisation_cropped.gif?t=1730066206\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the unforgiving Martian landscape, your colonists are your greatest resource. Manage a complex system of skills, traits, and relationships as you guide your crew through the challenges of off-world living. Monitor their physical health and mental states, ensuring they remain resilient in the face of adversity. Create a thriving community where each colonist's unique abilities contribute to the greater good of the colony.</